            Hi there! <br />
            I'm Maryam Akhyani, a software product manager with roots in
            design. I began my career in architecture and computational
            design, and my passion for technology led me to pivot into UX
            design and eventually product management. Over the past six years,
            I've been building SaaS products with a focus on creating
            efficient, human-centered experiences. Curious by nature, I'm
            always learning — from new languages to AI tools — and I thrive at
            the intersection of design, data, and empathy. At my core, I'm an
            idea generator, storyteller, and builder who believes that
            experiences matter more than products. This space is where I
            create meaningful experiences for real people, share my own
            journey, and experiment with new ideas. I don't shy away from
            getting my hands dirty, changing direction, or starting again —
            it's all part of the process. From here, you can connect with me
            or explore my work.
          </p>

